<normalizedToken id="B40ADA719EFD1B85A0A8742B581220B3" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2-4 
<normalizedToken id="7053AA85C8443D6A0C3E1B3502E9B847" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
; b) lunate to short falcate with a pointed apex and a somewhat flattened base, smooth- and thin-walled, 3-5-septate. Three-septate conidia: (16
<normalizedToken id="581D40FF75C1A45B6159A37D6BF48728" originalValue="–)18–27(–">-)18-27(-</normalizedToken>
